        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 48. Left valves and Zenker’s organ of species of the informal group ‘Macroscapha tensa-opaca’. Macroscapha cactus sp. nov.: A, holotype adult male (SNB 0041, ZMH K-41483); B, paratype adult male (SNB 0764); C, paratype adult male (SNB 0766) (ZMH K-40824). Macroscapha falcis sp. nov.: D, holotype adult female (SNB 0854, ZMH K-41497); E, paratype adult male (SNB 0471-DNA 178); F, paratype adult male (SNB 0493-DNA 200) (ZMH K-41496). Macroscapha solecavai sp. nov.: G, paratype adult female (SNB 0566-DNA273); H, paratype adult male (SNB 0563-DNA 271); I, paratype adult male (SNB 0561-DNA 268) (ZMH K-41499). Macroscapha sp. nov. 1: J, A (ZMH K-33305c). Macroscapha sp. cf. Macroscapha sp. nov. 1: K, A (ZMH K-33305b); O, adult male (SNB 0859, ZMH K-33305a). Macroscapha sp. nov. 2: L, A (ZMH K-34505a); P, adult male (SNB 0859, ZMH K-34505). Macroscapha sp.: M, N, A (ZMH K-34500); Q, adult male (SNB 0863, ZMH K-33928). A–N, left valve external view; O–Q, Zenker’s organ. Scale bars = 500 Mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4890172/files/figure.png" .

